title: Good but has annoying home feed refresh
text: On Android, the Google news feed only refreshes periodically (every hour maybe?) or if you pull to manually refresh. This app refreshes the home feed almost every time you open or switch to it, which is annoying if you’re trying to keep reading your feed or want to tap on the top article then it goes away because it refreshed. Please only refresh the feed if it’s been a while since it was loaded, or if I pull to refresh. And ideally refresh in the background so it doesn’t yank away news stories I’m about to select.
